        <li>Use the C key to cruise forward (to experience plane navigation).</li>
        <li>Use the Spacebar to make the lamp jump.</li>
        <li>Use the R key or the 'Reset Position' button to return to the default position.</li>
        <li>Use the F key or the 'Stop/Run' button to return to stop and start the lamp animation. After clicking either button, be sure to click outside the button.<br/>
